to take your pills.

10:47.429 --> 10:48.822
You keep them in
your right coat pocket.

10:48.865 --> 10:51.172
- Oh, okay.

10:51.215 --> 10:52.477
Where's my coat?
- It's down in my car.

10:52.521 --> 10:54.131
- Ah, I'll go get it.
You stay here.

10:54.175 --> 10:55.306
- No, no, no,
your penis is out.

10:55.350 --> 10:57.308
I'll go.
- Okay.

10:57.352 --> 11:00.181
Whew, boy, I love
that little guy, right?

11:00.224 --> 11:01.312
- Yeah.

11:02.531 --> 11:03.880
Oh, my phone's ringing.
Gotta grab it.

11:03.924 --> 11:05.142
It's Amy.
- Aw, Ames!

11:05.186 --> 11:06.187
Put her on FaceTime.

11:06.230 --> 11:07.797
- Wha?
No.

11:07.841 --> 11:09.886
- Come on!
- Hey, what's going on?

11:09.930 --> 11:11.540
- Hey, just checking in.

11:11.583 --> 11:13.150
How's it going with Charles?

11:13.194 --> 11:14.891
I know how hard
this is for you.

11:14.935 --> 11:15.979
Have you told him anything?

11:16.023 --> 11:17.154
- Nope, we're still all good.

11:17.198 --> 11:18.634
He has no idea that we are

11:18.678 --> 11:20.549
growing a Whomping Willow
in your Chamber of Secrets.

11:20.592 --> 11:22.507
- Well, I have to get back
to the seminar.

11:22.551 --> 11:24.248
Also, you've
ruined sex forever.

11:24.292 --> 11:25.293
- Yep, I heard it.

11:25.336 --> 11:26.294
I don't know why
I keep doing it.

11:26.337 --> 11:28.078
I love you. Bye.

11:28.122 --> 11:29.210
- What was all that about?

11:29.253 --> 11:30.951
- Oh, I actually
really can't tell you.

11:30.994 --> 11:32.517
No, wait a minute,
you're the only person

11:32.561 --> 11:33.823
that I can tell because
your brain's broken.

11:33.867 --> 11:35.216
Anything I say,
you'll just forget.

11:35.259 --> 11:36.739
- Well, I guess that's true.
Give it to me.

11:36.783 --> 11:38.132
- Amy and I are trying
to have a baby.

11:38.175 --> 11:41.135
- What?
Jake, that's wonderful.

11:41.178 --> 11:42.527
Come on, bring it in.

11:42.571 --> 11:44.181
- I'd rather not,
but it still feels really nice

11:44.225 --> 11:45.530
to talk to someone
about it finally.

11:45.574 --> 11:47.532
But I'm gonna be a dad.
It's so crazy.

11:47.576 --> 11:49.186
Hey, don't mention this
around Charles.

11:49.230 --> 11:51.188
Where am I?

11:51.232 --> 11:52.537
- Oh, perfect.

11:52.581 --> 11:54.844
- Listen, Denise,
I felt personally attacked

11:54.888 --> 11:57.151
when you included sesame bagels
at the bagel brunch

11:57.194 --> 11:58.543
knowing full well
I'm allergic.

11:58.587 --> 11:59.762
I developed a rash.

11:59.806 --> 12:00.807
- Says you, Ainsley.

12:00.850 --> 12:02.809
I believe food allergies
are a hoax.

12:02.852 --> 12:05.768
Perhaps your rash is from
all that makeup you wear.

12:05.812 --> 12:09.424
This is an office,
not some downtown dancery.

12:09.467 --> 12:10.860
- Okay, great.

12:10.904 --> 12:13.384
Now, in this roleplay, who can
tell me what went wrong?

12:13.428 --> 12:15.169
- Denise should have made
reasonable accommodations

12:15.212 --> 12:16.561
given Ainsley's
medical issue.

12:16.605 --> 12:18.476
