heightened the conflict

12:18.520 --> 12:20.435
by assuming that Denise
had a personal vendetta,

12:20.478 --> 12:21.741
and Denise shouldn't
have responded

12:21.784 --> 12:23.612
to Ainsley's complaint
with an ad hominem attack.

12:23.655 --> 12:25.135
- My thoughts exactly.
- I concur.

12:25.179 --> 12:27.094
- Yep.
- Wow.

12:27.137 --> 12:28.965
I'm really disappointed...

12:29.009 --> 12:31.185
that I have nothing
to correct you on.

12:31.228 --> 12:32.664
That was amazing.

12:32.708 --> 12:34.362
