12:34.405 --> 12:36.494
this entire seminar
that quickly before.

12:36.538 --> 12:38.801
It reminds me of
a really funny joke about--

12:38.845 --> 12:40.063
- Ha, ha, I'm laughing already.

12:40.107 --> 12:41.935
Great seminar, sad it's over,

12:41.978 --> 12:43.197
but it is, so see ya.

12:43.240 --> 12:44.807
- Actually,
I have good news.

12:44.851 --> 12:46.678
State law requires
that this seminar

12:46.722 --> 12:48.289
be no less than six hours,

12:48.332 --> 12:50.247
so I guess we'll spend
the next two hours

12:50.291 --> 12:51.901
diving into specific conflicts

12:51.945 --> 12:54.121
about this workplace
and solving them.

12:54.164 --> 12:55.644
- But we beat you.

12:55.687 --> 12:56.906
We beat you with study.

12:56.950 --> 12:58.734
- Brad, my funny friend,

12:58.778 --> 13:00.214
we don't need
this training.

13:00.257 --> 13:01.911
We don't have
any workplace conflicts.

13:01.955 --> 13:05.175
- Oh, there's always
conflict somewhere.

13:05.219 --> 13:08.918
Now, it could be something
small, like a pet peeve, or--

13:08.962 --> 13:11.616
- Hitchcock slept with my wife,
Kelly, in 1988!

13:11.660 --> 13:16.186
- So Kelly was his wife,
not his dog.

13:16.883 --> 13:18.710
- Hey, before Charles
gets back,

13:18.754 --> 13:20.234
