13:26.631 --> 13:28.503
Also, one time,
I ate a dog biscuit

13:28.546 --> 13:29.634
just to see
what it tasted like.

13:29.678 --> 13:31.114
- I get it.
They're delicious.

13:31.158 --> 13:32.289
- They're not bad.

13:32.333 --> 13:33.551
- Oh, here comes Charles.

13:33.595 --> 13:34.944
- Hey, man, did you get
Pimento's meds?

13:34.988 --> 13:36.641
- Sure did.
- Aw, thanks, Chuck.

13:36.685 --> 13:39.819
See, this is gonna make me
feel a lot better.

13:39.862 --> 13:41.951
- I grabbed you a water from
the hospital to wash 'em down.

13:41.995 --> 13:43.605
- Aw, thanks, Jake.

13:43.648 --> 13:44.911
You're gonna
make a good dad.

13:44.954 --> 13:47.304
I'm so glad you and Amy
are taking that step.

13:47.348 --> 13:48.784
- What? How did you--

13:48.828 --> 13:50.830
what about
your memory reset?

13:50.873 --> 13:52.570
