are trying to have a baby

13:52.614 --> 13:54.094
and you told Pimento
and not me?

13:55.225 --> 13:56.923
- They've got
a Panera here?

13:56.966 --> 14:00.404
Okay, I love their salads
exactly as they come.

14:00.448 --> 14:01.579
- Actually, you don't.

14:01.623 --> 14:02.711
Thanks, Jakey.

14:02.754 --> 14:05.235
See, you're gonna
make a great dad.

14:05.279 --> 14:06.715
- Stop saying that!

14:09.022 --> 14:10.414
- Hey.

14:10.458 --> 14:11.763
So you wanna talk about
