15:23.923 --> 15:24.967
Kelly was a real handful.

15:25.011 --> 15:26.360
- Wait, I'm confused again.

15:26.403 --> 15:28.449
Kelly was a dog?
- There were two Kellys.

15:28.492 --> 15:31.017
You'd know that if you'd
ever listened to my podcast.

15:31.060 --> 15:32.148
- Okay, dude, just relax.

15:32.192 --> 15:33.628
- Don't tell us to relax

15:33.671 --> 15:35.543
just because you're too nice
to have any pet peeves.

15:35.586 --> 15:37.240
- Oh, Terry's got peeves.

15:37.284 --> 15:39.460
Terry hates the way you always
make mouth noises when you eat.

15:39.503 --> 15:41.723
Nom, nom, I'm Rosa.
I'm eating a croissant.

15:41.766 --> 15:42.985
Nom, nom.

15:43.029 --> 15:44.595
- How's this for a mouth noise?
You suck.

15:44.639 --> 15:45.683
- No, you suck!

15:45.727 --> 15:47.381
- As do you, as do you and you!

15:47.424 --> 15:49.644
- Oh, yeah? Well,
you're all a bunch of flopes.

15:49.687 --> 15:51.124
- Flopes?
