15:54.475 --> 15:55.519
- Okay, all right.

15:55.563 --> 15:58.566
Okay, guys,
that is our six hours.

15:58.609 --> 16:00.263
The seminar is over.

16:00.307 --> 16:02.091
I'm really proud of you guys,

16:02.135 --> 16:04.006
lots of good progress
here today.

16:04.050 --> 16:05.399
You're welcome.

16:05.442 --> 16:08.054
- I'm Detective Boyle.
This is my partner, Jake.

16:08.097 --> 16:09.185
You probably think it's weird

16:09.229 --> 16:10.578
that I said partner
and not friend.

16:10.621 --> 16:11.927
- Not at all.
- Well, the point is

16:11.971 --> 16:13.755
that we're strictly
colleagues.

16:13.798 --> 16:15.235
Have you seen this man?

16:15.278 --> 16:17.585
- Yeah, he was here a few
hours ago for a new tattoo.

16:17.628 --> 16:18.716
It was supposed to say,

16:18.760 --> 16:19.717
"Jake and Amy are trying
to have a baby."

16:19.761 --> 16:21.415
- Seriously?
- Aw.

16:21.458 --> 16:22.807
Wait a minute, what do you mean
"supposed to"?

16:22.851 --> 16:24.113
- He jumped out of the chair
before I could finish,

16:24.157 --> 16:25.593
second time
it's happened.

16:25.636 --> 16:26.724
First time, he left
with a tat that said,

16:26.768 --> 16:27.899
"Don't trust your D."

16:27.943 --> 16:29.336
- That wasn't the whole tattoo?
- No.

16:29.379 --> 16:30.772
He wanted it to say,
"Don't trust your doctor."

16:30.815 --> 16:32.339
- Oh, my God.

16:32.382 --> 16:34.950
Pimento's doctor
is trying to kill him.

16:34.994 --> 16:36.386
He must have remembered
something

16:36.430 --> 16:37.605
when he stopped
taking his pills.

16:37.648 --> 16:38.867
The pills are what's messing
with his memory.

16:38.910 --> 16:40.347
- We have to find him
before his doctor does.

16:40.390 --> 16:41.957
- Oh, I know where he's going.
- You do? Where?

16:42.001 --> 16:43.045
- Said he's going
to his doctor.

16:43.089 --> 16:44.438
- Oh.

16:45.830 --> 16:47.180
Thanks.

16:48.007 --> 16:50.270
- Detectives,
good to see you again.

16:50.313 --> 16:52.141
- Oh, I see, the villain
playing it cool

16:52.185 --> 16:53.751
when confronted
by the good guys,

16:53.795 --> 16:56.145
just like Javier Bardem
in "No Country for Old Men."

16:58.147 --> 16:59.844
Do you guys only watch
kids' movies?

16:59.888 --> 17:03.544
- Whatever you're insinuating,
I assure you, you're incorrect.

17:03.587 --> 17:04.936
- Cut the crap, Doc.
